Class SheetOutputter

  • java.lang.Object
    • write.SheetOutputter

  • public class SheetOutputter
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to output the loaded information from P6 to CSV files. Each table exported has it's own CSV file. Files currently supported: Timesheets Resource ResourceHour ResourceRate TimesheetPeriod.
